---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Hogar Gallán • Casa Rural en Gondomar, Galicia" description="Escápate a Hogar Gallán, chalet exclusivo para 8 personas con piscina privada en las Rías Baixas. Reserva directa con mejor precio y experiencia personalizada.">
  
  <!-- Navbar -->
  <nav class="bg-white border-b border-[#e5d9c8] sticky top-0 z-50">
    <div class="max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto px-8 py-5 flex items-center justify-between">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-x-3">
        <div class="w-9 h-9 bg-[#1a3c34] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
          <span class="text-white text-xl font-bold tracking-tighter">HG</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="font-bold text-2xl tracking-[-1.5px] text-[#1a3c34]">Hogar Gallán</div>
          <div class="text-[10px] text-[#8a7560] -mt-1 tracking-[1px]">GONDOMAR • GALICIA</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="hidden md:flex items-center gap-x-9 text-sm font-medium">
        <a href="#sobre" class="hover:text-[#c9a16e] transition-colors">El Alojamiento</a>
        <a href="#galeria" class="hover:text-[#c9a16e] transition-colors">Galería</a>
        <a href="#disponibilidad" class="hover:text-[#c9a16e] transition-colors">Disponibilidad</a>
        <a href="#como-reservar" class="hover:text-[#c9a16e] transition-colors">Cómo reservar</a>
      </div>

      <div class="flex items-center gap-x-3">
        <button onclick="document.getElementById('gestor-modal').classList.remove('hidden'); document.getElementById('gestor-modal').classList.add('flex')"
                class="hidden md:flex items-center gap-x-2 px-5 py-2.5 text-xs font-semibold tracking-wider border border-[#1a3c34] text-[#1a3c34] rounded-full hover:bg-[#1a3c34] hover:text-white transition-colors">
          <span>GESTOR</span>
        </button>
        
        <a href="#disponibilidad" 
           class="bg-[#1a3c34] hover:bg-[#142d27] text-white text-sm font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-full flex items-center gap-x-2 shadow-lg transition-colors">
          RESERVAR AHORA
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <header class="h-[100dvh] min-h-[640px] flex items-center relative bg-cover bg-center" 
          style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(26, 60, 52, 0.35), rgba(26, 60, 52, 0.45)), url('/images/001 house.jpg')">
    <div class="max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto px-8 pt-16">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-x-2 bg-white/90 backdrop-blur px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full mb-6 text-xs tracking-[2px] font-semibold text-[#1a3c34]">
          <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-emerald-500 rounded-full animate-pulse"></div>
          DISPONIBLE • TEMPORADA 2026
        </div>
        
        <h1 class="text-[72px] md:text-[86px] leading-[0.92] tracking-[-4.5px] text-white mb-4 font-bold">
          Tu refugio<br>en las Rías Baixas
        </h1>
        
        <p class="max-w-md text-lg text-white/90 mb-9">
          Chalet exclusivo para 8 personas con piscina privada, jardín y vistas a la sierra. 
          A 15 minutos de las mejores playas de Galicia.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
          <a href="#disponibilidad" 
             class="group inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-x-3 bg-white text-[#1a3c34] hover:bg-[#f8f1e9] font-semibold px-9 py-4 rounded-2xl text-base shadow-xl transition-all">
            Comprobar disponibilidad
          </a>
          
          <button onclick="window.open('https://wa.me/34617345289?text=Hola%2C%20estoy%20interesado%20en%20reservar%20Hogar%20Gall%C3%A1n', '_blank')"
                  class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-x-3 border-2 border-white/70 hover:bg-white/10 text-white font-medium px-8 py-4 rounded-2xl text-base backdrop-blur transition">
            Hablar por WhatsApp
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- SOBRE -->
  <section id="sobre" class="max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto px-8 pt-20 pb-16">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-x-12 gap-y-12 items-center">
      <div class="lg:col-span-7">
        <div class="uppercase tracking-[3px] text-xs font-semibold text-[#c9a16e] mb-3">DESDE 2021 • VUT-PO-005628</div>
        <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl leading-none tracking-[-2.5px] text-[#1a3c34] mb-6">Una casa con alma<br>en el corazón de Galicia</h2>
        
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-[#3f3730] text-[17px] leading-relaxed">
          <p>Hogar Gallán es mucho más que un alojamiento. Es un refugio privado de 400 m² rodeado de naturaleza, donde el tiempo se detiene. Ubicado en la Serra do Galiñeiro, a solo 15 minutos de las playas de las Rías Baixas y 20 minutos de Vigo.</p>
          <p class="mt-4">Con 4 dormitorios, 3 baños, cocina totalmente equipada, piscina privada, zona de barbacoa y amplios espacios interiores y exteriores, es el lugar ideal para familias, grupos de amigos o escapadas románticas.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-x-2 bg-white border border-[#e5d9c8] px-5 h-11 rounded-2xl text-sm">
            <span class="font-medium">Hasta 8 personas</span>
          </div>
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-x-2 bg-white border border-[#e5d9c8] px-5 h-11 rounded-2xl text-sm">
            <span class="font-medium">400 m² de exclusividad</span>
          </div>
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-x-2 bg-white border border-[#e5d9c8] px-5 h-11 rounded-2xl text-sm">
            <span class="font-medium">Piscina privada</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="lg:col-span-5">
        <img src="/images/002 house.jpg" 
             class="w-full h-[420px] object-cover rounded-3xl shadow-2xl border border-white" 
             alt="Hogar Gallán - Casa de piedra con piscina privada">
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- GALERÍA -->
  <section id="galeria" class="bg-white py-16 border-y border-[#e5d9c8]">
    <div class="max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-10">
        <div class="text-[#c9a16e] text-xs tracking-[2.5px] font-semibold">DESCUBRE EL ESPACIO</div>
        <h3 class="text-4xl tracking-[-1.5px] text-[#1a3c34] mt-2">Galería de Hogar Gallán</h3>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
        <div class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl aspect-[4/3] shadow-md">
          <img src="/images/001 house.jpg" class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-110" alt="Fachada principal">
          <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/70 p-4 text-white text-sm font-semibold">Casa principal • Piscina privada</div>
        </div>
        <div class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl aspect-[4/3] shadow-md">
          <img src="/images/002 pool.jpg" class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-110" alt="Piscina privada">
          <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/70 p-4 text-white text-sm font-semibold">Piscina privada • Solárium</div>
        </div>
        <div class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl aspect-[4/3] shadow-md">
          <img src="/images/0003 outside.jpg" class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-110" alt="Terraza">
          <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/70 p-4 text-white text-sm font-semibold">Terraza con vistas</div>
        </div>
        <div class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl aspect-[4/3] shadow-md">
          <img src="/images/0003 interior.jpg" class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-110" alt="Salón">
          <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/70 p-4 text-white text-sm font-semibold">Salón principal</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CARACTERÍSTICAS -->
  <section class="max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto px-8 py-16">
    <div class="flex justify-between items-end mb-10">
      <div>
        <div class="text-[#c9a16e] text-xs tracking-[2.5px] font-semibold">TODO INCLUIDO</div>
        <h3 class="text-4xl tracking-[-1.5px] text-[#1a3c34]">Lo que encontrarás</h3>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-4 xl:grid-cols-5 gap-4">
      <div class="amenity-card bg-[#f8f5f0] p-6 rounded-3xl border border-[#e5d9c8]">
        <div class="text-3xl mb-4">🏊</div>
        <div class="font-semibold text-lg">Piscina privada</div>
        <div class="text-sm text-[#6b6259] mt-1">Uso exclusivo • Solárium • Vistas a la sierra</div>
      </div>
      <!-- ... resto de tarjetas ... -->
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- DISPONIBILIDAD -->
  <section id="disponibilidad" class="max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto px-8 py-20">
    <!-- ... formulario ... -->
  </section>

</Layout>
